  "title": "test: Testing stack + `Hit` and `Template` tests",
  "body": "The testing stack is ready.\n\nIt's composed of:\n- karma\n- mocha\n- expect (assertions)\n\nChanges in npm scripts:\n- `test` now runs the tests in phantomjs and then lint\n- `test:watch` will open a real chrome canary, output results in terminal console and auto reload tests\n\nIt's basically the stack from https://github.com/rackt/react-router/ with some modifications.\n\nI wrote the `Hits` and `Template` tests, they may not be exhaustive but that's a start. Once we get this merged I will create the relevant issues so that anyone can help in writing tests.\n\nWe need to strengthen this library because untested code will and must #fail.\n\nTODO:\n- [ ] port test/ folder to karma, mocha, expect\n",
